<br />Hello, my star <span class="st">☆</span><br />
<br />I just wanted to say a few words, please read this!<br />
<br />I can&rsquo;t remember when i started to like you. and it&rsquo;s confusing how we ended up so close.<br />
<br />i can&rsquo;t remember when we started sleeping side by side. or when we started living together.<br />
<br />or when we conceived this 6 week old baby in my tummy. ok i was kidding about that last one it&rsquo;s clearly 6 weeks ago.<br />
<br />i can still remember how i felt when you said &ldquo;i love you&rdquo; for the first time but i also can&rsquo;t remember when.<br />
<br />and i want us to have a definitive when because it&rsquo;s an excuse to spoil you.<br />
<br />a when that we&rsquo;ll both remember in the future i hope.<br />
<br />so, if you would take my heart today and be my boyfriend for realsies, i hope this can be our anniversary date.<br />
<br />would you like to be my boyfriend?<br />
<br />From your baby,<br />
jieun<br />
